.TH sfm 1 sfm\-VERSION
.SH NAME
sfm \- a simple file manager for unix-like systems
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B sfm
.RB [ \-v ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
sfm is a simple file manager based on termbox.
.P
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-v
print version.
.SH USAGE
.TP
.B q
quit
.TP
.B h
back
.TP
.B j
down
.TP
.B k
up
.TP
.B l
open dir|file
.TP
.B g
top
.TP
.B G
bottom
.TP
.B ctrl+u
scroll up
.TP
.B ctrl+d
scroll down
.TP
.B /
start filter
.TP
.B ENTER
find filter
.TP
.B ESC
exit filter
.TP
.B SPACE
switch pane
.SH CUSTOMIZATION
sfm is customized by creating a custom config.h and (re)compiling the source
code. This keeps it fast, secure and simple.
